content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Aug 19 (APP):The Senate session commenced at 11:08 a.m. on Tuesday under the deputy chairmanship of Deputy Chairman Syedaal Khan Nasar. The House was set to take up various agenda items, including the Question Hour, motions, legislative business, a resolution for the extension of an ordinance, presentation of reports, and a calling attention notice.
